<p>2nd MWIA Latin America Regional Congress i samarbejde med Pan American Medical Women's Alliance 25-29 october 2000, Panama City, Panama, Central America<br />Emne: XXIst Centery - a New Ligestyle<br />E-mail: <a href="mailto:ceciliamela63@hotmail.com"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #0066cc;">ceciliamela63@hotmail.com</span></span></a> <span style="display: none;"></p>
